    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel worth it. there isn't anything left for me. it's like i'm just a ghost haunting this house. i keep thinking about how he's in a better place, somewhere peaceful, and he's not in pain anymore. part of me thinks it would be so much more peaceful if i could just be with him. like, wouldn't it finally make sense if we were together again?",
